{"type":"message","id":"ba9d9b10","parentId":"d642f975","timestamp":"2026-05-20T18:25:40.914Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So there's already usage of `apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/devices/' + ip + '/credentials')` elsewhere in the code. This means the credentials API is a GET endpoint that returns credentials without needing authentication. The issue is specifically in the `connectDevice` function where it hardcodes `username: 'admin', password: ''`.\n\nLet me re-read the task. The task says:\n- Current code hardcodes `username: 'admin', password: ''` causing WASM SDK login failure\n- Fix: First get credentials via `apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/devices/' + ip + '/credentials')`, then use those credentials in the connect POST\n\n\n- Now I need to locate the `connectDevice` function in the base.html file to apply this fix.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"The credentials GET endpoint is already used elsewhere in the codebase and works without auth. The issue is specifically in `connectDevice()` which hardcodes credentials. Let me apply the fix.\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1b70c785eec14799a05d3865","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\fix_connect.js","content":"const fs = require('fs');\nconst path = 'D:/astro_py/astro_hub/src/web/base.html';\nlet content = fs.readFileSync(path, 'utf8');\n\nconst searchStart = 'function connectDevice(ip) {';\nconst searchEnd = '        function connectDeviceWithCreds';\n\nconst s = content.indexOf(searchStart);\nconst e = content.indexOf(searchEnd, s);\n\nif (s === -1 || e === -1) {\n  console.error('Could not find function boundaries');\n  process.exit(1);\n}\n\nconst oldFunc = content.substring(s, e);\nconsole.log('Found function at', s, 'to', e, '(length:', oldFunc.length, ')');\n\nconst newFunc = `function connectDevice(ip) {\n            addLog('info', 'ж≠£еЬ®ињЮжО•иЃЊе§З: ' + ip);\n            // еЕИиОЈеПЦ credentials\n            apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/devices/' + ip + '/credentials').then(function(creds) {\n                var username = (creds && creds.success) ? creds.username : 'admin';\n                var password = (creds && creds.success) ? creds.password : '';\n                var port = (creds && creds.success) ? (creds.port || 80) : 80;\n\n                // еЖНи∞ГзФ® connect API\n                apiPost('/api/v1/devices/' + ip + '/connect', { username: username, password: password, port: port }).then(function(result) {\n                    if (result && result.success) {\n                        showToast('success', 'иЃЊе§ЗеЈ≤ињЮжО•: ' + ip);\n                        addLog('success', result.message || 'ињЮжО•жИРеКЯ');\n                        refreshDevices();\n                        refreshPtzDeviceList();\n                        refreshAdvancedDeviceSelectors();\n                        // Update global window.connectedDevice\n                        var dev = allDevices.find(function(d) { return d.ip === ip; });\n                        if (dev) {\n                            window.connectedDevice = {\n                                ip: dev.ip, model: dev.model || '', name: dev.name || dev.device_name || '',\n                                mac: dev.mac || '', username: username, password: password, port: port, online: true\n                            };\n                            addLog('info', 'еЈ≤иЃ∞дљПињЮжО•иЃЊе§З: ' + window.connectedDevice.ip);\n                            // WASM SDK login\n                            if (window.clickLogin2) { window.clickLogin2(); }\n                        }\n                    } else if (result && result.message && result.message.indexOf('еЗ≠иѓБ') >= 0) {\n                        // credentials йФЩиѓѓпЉМжПРз§ЇзФ®жИЈиЊУеЕ•\n                        var username2 = prompt(\"иѓЈиЊУеЕ•зФ®жИЈеРН:\", \"admin\");\n                        if (!username2) return;\n                        var password2 = prompt(\"иѓЈиЊУеЕ•еѓЖз†Б:\");\n                        if (!password2) return;\n                        connectDeviceWithCreds(ip, username2, password2, 80);\n                    } else {\n                        showToast('error', result ? result.message : 'ињЮжО•е§±иі•');\n                        addLog('error', result ? result.message : 'ињЮжО•е§±иі•');\n                    }\n                }).catch(function(e) {\n                    showToast('error', 'ињЮжО•еЉВеЄЄ: ' + e.message);\n                    addLog('error', 'ињЮжО•еЉВеЄЄ: ' + e.message);\n                });\n            }).catch(function(e) {\n                // credentials API е§±иі•пЉМе∞ЭиѓХжЧ†еѓЖз†БињЮжО•\n                apiPost('/api/v1/devices/' + ip + '/connect', null).then(function(result) {\n                    if (result && result.success) {\n                        showToast('success', 'иЃЊе§ЗеЈ≤ињЮжО•: ' + ip);\n                        refreshDevices();\n                        refreshPtzDeviceList();\n                        refreshAdvancedDeviceSelectors();\n                        var dev = allDevices.find(function(d) { return d.ip === ip; });\n                        if (dev) {\n                            window.connectedDevice = {\n                                ip: dev.ip, model: dev.model || '', name: dev.name || dev.device_name || '',\n                                mac: dev.mac || '', username: 'admin', password: '', port: 80, online: true\n                            };\n                            if (window.clickLogin2) { window.clickLogin2(); }\n                        }\n                    } else {\n                        showToast('error', result ? result.message : 'ињЮжО•е§±иі•');\n                    }\n                });\n            });\n        }\n\n        `;\n\ncontent = content.substring(0, s) + newFunc + content.substring(e);\nfs.writeFileSync(path, content, 'utf8');\nconsole.log('DONE. Replaced connectDevice function.');\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"YerPlan","model":"qwen3.6-plus","usage":{"input":26512,"output":1210,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27722,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779301517654,"responseId":"chatcmpl-6eaec2b2-4d5c-9210-93da-fec67a74bead"}}
